{
  "stem": "18486.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 394.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he said, oh, we-- I'm burying a dead rabbit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then I saw the package with the tar paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said that's a very honorable thing, to be buried that way, for a rabbit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Is that really a rabbit?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then my husband said, well, as far as you've seen us-- it's a rabbit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't tell things each other what we did, because the least you know, the better you were off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he said, I didn't want you to know, but it is the package.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there is danger in the village today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we had that package.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were also stamps from the German leader we had stolen.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Not we, ourselves, but in our group, they had stolen stamps, which we used to falsify papers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then there was a raid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they came to this friend who had had that package and used the stamps.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they-- they took him, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said, we know that you have those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, well, I don't have those.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've never seen them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, he denied it, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then they-- my husband had gone there just before they came to him, because they had been to somebody-- how did we know-- that I don't remember exactly.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But I know that my husband went just before they came and got the package out of his house and buried it in our garden.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then when they started to torture him-- well, who was it again?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, yeah, when they tortured him, finally he couldn't stand it any longer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they put weights in his ear lobes, that his ear lobes were hanging till here, you know, and-- This is Jan--",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That is Jan Bartelsman.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
